data.description: Welcome to your dream mountain retreat located in Roosevelt National Park, nestled between Boulder and Estes Park!This remodeled home offers an unparalleled combination of breathtaking views, modern amenities,& designer architecture.Step inside & prepare to be captivated by the stunning interior that seamlessly blends contemporary elements with the charm of mtn living.This floor plan creates a sense of spaciousness,allowing natural light to flood every corner of the home.The living area boasts soaring ceilings, accentuated by large windows that frame the awe-inspiring mountain vistas.Indulge in the warmth & coziness of 2 wood-burning fireplaces, perfect for those chilly winter evenings.The crackling of the fire will provide the perfect ambiance as you unwind after a day of hiking or skiing.The heart of the home is a fully equipped gourmet kitchen,featuring top-of-the-line appliances,sleek countertops, double ovens & a wet bar.Whether you're a chef or a culinary enthusiast, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary creativity.Addt'l highlights of this remarkable home include heated floors to provide warmth & comfort during the colder months,& a wrap-around deck that invites you to savor the beauty of the surrounding landscape.Whether you're entertaining guests or relaxing in solitude, the deck offers the perfect vantage point to soak in the awe-inspiring vistas.The location of this mountain haven couldn't be more ideal.With the Ceran St. Vrain Trail and Brainard Lake and Rocky Mtn State Park just mins away, you'll have easy access to a myriad of outdoor activities, including hiking, biking,& horseback riding.Being situated between Boulder/Estes,you'll have the best of both worlds:the vibrant cultural scene & amenities of Boulder,& the captivating natural beauty & tourism of Estes Park.Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a fully remodeled mountain home with breathtaking views, designer architecture, and proximity to outdoor adventures.Your mtn paradise awaits!
